  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SHTREK is a simple but challenging platformer where every move matters. You have <strong>60 levels</strong> to beat and <strong>60 lives</strong> to do it. No extra mechanics, no distractions - just precise jumps, fast resets, and pure platforming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503510/extras/4419703160d3c24921bf951523c56478.poster.avif?t=1741283243\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503510/extras/4419703160d3c24921bf951523c56478.webm?t=1741283243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503510/extras/4419703160d3c24921bf951523c56478.mp4?t=1741283243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SHTREK is built for speed and precision.  Track your best runs with the highscore board and keep pushing for a faster time. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>60 levels, 60 lives</strong> - A focused platforming challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Minimalist, clean visuals</strong> - Nothing but you, the obstacles, and the goal.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speedrunner-friendly</strong> - Keep track of your best runs and improve over time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Instant respawns</strong> - No waiting, just move.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Secrets</strong> - Discover hidden levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Music</strong> - It's nice.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
